<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.6">
<l>ēṉa māynilaṅ kīṇṭave ṉappaṉē kaṇṇā veṉṟu meṉṉai yāḷuṭai</l>
<l>vāṉanā yakaṉē maṇimā ṇikkac cuṭarē</l>
<l>tēṉa māmpoḻi ṟaṇcirī varamaṅkalat tavarkkai toḻavuṟai</l>
<l>vāṉa māmalai yēvaṭi yēṉṟoḻa vantaruḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My father, who split the ground as a boar, Kṛṣṇa, heaven’s leader</l>
<l>who always has me as a servant, glow of gem ruby,</l>
<l>celestial great mountain who stays while the people of Cirīvaramaṅkalam cool with groves of honeyed mango tress</l>
<l>worship [you], hands [folded], graciously come for me, [your] servant, to worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
